headline: Instagram to Limit Content for Teenage Users Based on PG-13 Ratings
summary: Instagram is rolling out new protections for teenagers’ accounts and introducing a system that limits what young users can see based on PG-13 movie ratings.  Teen Instagram users by default will be able to access content similar to what they might see in a PG-13 movie, Instagram said Tuesday.  Under the new limits, Instagram said it would hide certain content like strong language, risky stunts and marijuana-related content from teen users.
